@* Razor View (cshtml) *@

@* Description:
The code is an HTML Page with "razor" mark-up *@


@*specifies the URL of this component.*@
@page "/"  


@namespace FirstBlazorApp.Pages
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.Web

@* import the tag helper in the component. *@
@addTagHelper *, Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers


@* Đây chính là trang html tổng vì nó có DOCTYPE,... *@
@* Nó giống với index.html trong các front-end framework khác *@
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

@* Inside the head section we call HeadOutlet component  *@
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blazor First App</title>
    <base href="~/" /> @* The "base html tag" specifies the base URL, which is root url, for all relative URLs on the app. *@

    @* HeadOutlet renders content provided by PageTitle and HeadContent components. *@
    @* In short, it will help to set the page titles, metas, etc on the html head section for different razor components. *@
    <component type="typeof(HeadOutlet)" render-mode="ServerPrerendered" />

    @* ServerPrerendered It tells to render the component into static HTML and includes a marker for a Blazor server-side application *@
    @* The HTML content of the component is sent again over the persistent HTTP connection. *@
    @* nói tóm lại mode ServerPrerendered thực hiện 2 hành động
    1 : Nó sẽ render các component thành HTML tĩnh và gửi đến browser
    2 : Sao khi HTML tĩnh được gửi đến browser thì Blazor tiếp tục thực hiện 1 kết nối SignalR từ browser -> server
        Mục đích của bước thứ 2 là để kích hoạt các chức năng để tường tác (vd: xử lý sự kiện khi click) *@


    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

    @* Next, inside the body, we calls Blazor Router component which is defined by the App.razor as shown below: *@
    <div class="m-1 p-1">
        <h1>Hello World!</h1>
        

        @* Call the component we want to render, which is App *@
        @* Trong _Host.cshtml gọi App component, giống như front-end _framework khác *@
        @* Vd trong ReactJS trong index.html gọi App component *@
        <component type="typeof(App)" render-mode="ServerPrerendered" />
    </div>


    @* The script element specifies the name of the JavaScript file that establishes the SignalR connection with the server. *@
    @* Note that you “don’t” have to add this JavaScript file to the project as it will be done automatically by Blazor. *@
    <script src="_framework/blazor.server.js"></script>
</body>
</html>